results.name: Decimal expansion of Product_{k>=1} (1 + 1/k^8).
formula: Equals (cos(sqrt(4 - 2*sqrt(2))*Pi) + cos(sqrt(4 + 2*sqrt(2))*Pi) + cosh(sqrt(4 - 2*sqrt(2))*Pi) + cosh(sqrt(4 + 2*sqrt(2))*Pi) - 2*cos(sqrt(2 - sqrt(2))*Pi) * cosh(sqrt(2 - sqrt(2))*Pi) - 2*cos(sqrt(2 + sqrt(2))*Pi) * cosh(sqrt(2 + sqrt(2))*Pi)) / (8*Pi^4).
results.author: _Vaclav Kotesovec_, Apr 27 2020
